      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_kaya_2_lua_Description"                                                                          "<h1>Passive: Staff</h1> Increases your magical damage by %spell_amplify%%% per intelligence point<br><br>Effect does not work on percentage damage<br><br>Item effectiveness reduced to 20% if target is enemy hero"
