      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven"                                                                       "Torture Pipe I"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_Description"                                                           "<h1>Passive: Unstable Affliction</h1>Significantly increases your damage from spells dealing periodic damage per attribute point<br><br><b>Press ALT for detailed information</b>"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_Note0"                                                                 "Ability amplification from identical items does not stack"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_Note1"                                                                 "If ability target is enemy hero, item effectiveness reduced to 35%."
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_Note2"                                                                 "Amplifies the following abilities and items: Acid Spray, Battle Hunger, Bramble Maze, Burning Spear, Celestial Hammer, Chakram, Chaos Meteor, Cinder Brew, Cold Feet, Corrosive Skin, Crippling Fear, Curse of the Forest, Curse of the Silent, Dark Pact, Dismember, Doom, Dual Breath, Dying Light, Epicenter, Fallen Sky, Fiend's Grip, Fire Remnant, Fire Spirits, Fireball, Firefly, Flame Guard, Flamebreak, Flamethrower, Flaming Lasso, Flux, Frost Shield, Frostbite, Giant's Ring, Hellfire Blast, Icarus Dive, Ice Vortex, Ignite, Immolation, Ion Shell, Leech Seed, Life Drain, Liquid Fire, Macropyre, Magnetize, Meteor Hammer, Nature's Grasp, Nethertoxin, Overgrowth, Poison Attack, Poison Sting, Poison Touch, Psionic Trap, Radiance, Rot, Sand Storm, Scorched Earth, Searing Chains, Second Chakram, Shackles, Shadow Poison, Shadow Strike, Shadow Word, Shrapnel, Silken Bola, Solar Guardian, Spirit Walk, Static Storm, Thunder Strike, Upheaval, Urn of Shadows, Venomous Gale, Viper Strike, Voodoo Restoration"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_bonus_all_stats"                                                       "+$all"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_bonus_health"                                                          "+$health"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_1_datadriven_bonus_mana_regen"                                                      "+$mana_regen"
