      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_hydras_breath_ability_note"                                                                     "Does not affect Roshan or Nian"
      "INSTA_KILL_NOTE"                                                                                                          "Deals damage to creeps equal to 100% of their maximum HP. Each curse on the losing side reduces this damage by 20%. Targeted insta-kill abilities don't work on creeps summoned by other players."
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_torture_pipe_2_datadriven_Note2"                                                                 "Amplifies the following abilities and items: Acid Spray, Battle Hunger, Bramble Maze, Burning Spear, Celestial Hammer, Chakram, Chaos Meteor, Cinder Brew, Cold Feet, Corrosive Skin, Crippling Fear, Curse of the Forest, Curse of the Silent, Dark Pact, Dismember, Doom, Dual Breath, Dying Light, Epicenter, Fallen Sky, Fiend's Grip, Fire Remnant, Fire Spirits, Fireball, Firefly, Flame Guard, Flamebreak, Flamethrower, Flaming Lasso, Flux, Frost Shield, Frostbite, Giant's Ring, Hellfire Blast, Icarus Dive, Ice Vortex, Ignite, Immolation, Ion Shell, Leech Seed, Life Drain, Liquid Fire, Macropyre, Magnetize, Meteor Hammer, Nature's Grasp, Nethertoxin, Overgrowth, Poison Attack, Poison Sting, Poison Touch, Psionic Trap, Radiance, Rot, Sand Storm, Scorched Earth, Searing Chains, Second Chakram, Shackles, Shadow Poison, Shadow Strike, Shadow Word, Shrapnel, Silken Bola, Solar Guardian, Spirit Walk, Static Storm, Thunder Strike, Upheaval, Urn of Shadows, Venomous Gale, Viper Strike, Voodoo Restoration"
