      "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_dagon_4_custom"                                                                                  "Dagon"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dagon_4_custom_Description"                                                                      "<h1>Active: Energy Burst</h1> Releases a powerful energy burst, dealing magical damage to selected enemy unit.<br><br>Disables <b><font color='#53ea48'>passive</font></b> abilities of selected target for %duration% sec.<br><br>Damage: %damage%<br>Cast range: %abilitycastrange%<br>Mana cost: %mana_cost_tooltip%"
      "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dagon_4_custom_Lore"                                                                             "A magic wand that grows stronger over time, granting owner magic at their fingertips."
