    "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_timber_spider_death_whirling_Description"                                                               "Spins in a deadly whirl, dealing %damage% pure damage to enemies within %whirling_radius%. If trees are nearby, damage increases to %damage_with_tree% and stuns enemies for %stun_with_tree% sec. Destroys trees in the radius."
