     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_satyr_trickster"                                                                  "Satyr Banisher"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_satyr_trickster_Description"                                                      "<h1>Active: Summon</h1>Summons Satyr Banisher for all enemies in the next round.\n<font color='#f00'>Has the Purge ability, which removes positive effects from the target.</font>\n<font color='#f00'>Summoning becomes available after round %summon_round% (default settings) or if 4 or fewer players remain. Current game settings can be viewed in «Menu» > «Settings» > «Current Game Settings».</font>"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_warpine"                                                                          "Warpine Raider"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_warpine_Description"                                                              "<h1>Active: Summon</h1>Summons Warpine Raider for all enemies in the next round.\n<font color='#f00'>Summoning becomes available after round %summon_round% (default settings) or if 4 or fewer players remain. Current game settings can be viewed in «Menu» > «Settings» > «Current Game Settings».</font>"

     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_siltbreaker"                                                                      "Siltbreaker"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_siltbreaker_Description"                                                          "<h1>Active: Summon</h1>Summons Siltbreaker for all enemies in the next round.<br><font color='#f00'>Has the Evasion Aura ability, which increases evasion of all allied creeps by 40%.</font>\n<font color='#f00'>Summoning becomes available after round %summon_round% (default settings) or if 4 or fewer players remain. Current game settings can be viewed in «Menu» > «Settings» > «Current Game Settings».</font>"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_roshling_big"                                                                     "Golden Roshling"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_roshling_big_Description"                                                         "<h1>Active: Summon</h1>Summons Golden Roshling for all enemies in the next round.\n<font color='#f00'>Summoning becomes available after round %summon_round% (default settings) or if 4 or fewer players remain. Current game settings can be viewed in «Menu» > «Settings» > «Current Game Settings».</font>"
       
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_big_thunder_lizard"                                                               "Thunder Lizard"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_big_thunder_lizard_Description"                                                   "<h1>Active: Summon</h1>Summons Thunder Lizard for all enemies in the next round.\n<font color='#f00'>Has the War Drums Aura ability, which increases accuracy of all allied creeps by 51%.</font>\n<font color='#f00'>Summoning becomes available after round %summon_round% (default settings) or if 4 or fewer players remain. Current game settings can be viewed in «Menu» > «Settings» > «Current Game Settings».</font>"      
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_spider_range"                                                                     "Toxin Spider"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_extra_creature_spider_range_Description"                                                         "<h1>Active: Summon</h1>Summons Toxin Spider for all enemies in the next round.\n<font color='#f00'>Has the Nethertoxin ability, which disables passive abilities.</font>\n<font color='#f00'>Summoning becomes available after round %summon_round% (default settings) or if 4 or fewer players remain. Current game settings can be viewed in «Menu» > «Settings» > «Current Game Settings».</font>"        
