     "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_ninja_gear_custom"                                                                               "Ninja Gear"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_ninja_gear_custom_Description"                                                                   "<h1>Active: Solitary Disguise</h1>Invisibility for %duration% sec. Attacks do not break invisibility, but it ends if an enemy hero appears within 1200 range. Reduces all outgoing damage by 25%% while active.\n\n<h1>Stats:</h1>+%bonus_agility% agility<br>+%passive_movement_bonus%%% movement speed"
     "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_ninja_gear_custom_Lore"                                                                          "Precious equipment found by a young explorer in the wreckage and ruins floating in the endless void."
