     "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_ninja_gear_custom_Description"                                                                       "Invisible, +25 move speed, hidden from the enemy minimap. Getting within 1200 range of an enemy hero reveals the invisibility (except while defending creeps on your own arena)."
