 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_hand_of_midas_custom_Lore"                                                                           "Preserved through unknown forces, the Hand of Midas is a weapon of greed, sacrificing animals to line the owner's pockets."
 "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_hand_of_midas_custom_Description"                                                                    "<h1>Active: Transmute</h1> Kills target non-hero unit, granting %bonus_gold% gold and %xp_multiplier% times experience. <br><br>Cast Range: %abilitycastrange%"
