   "LastDuelLabel"                                                                                                               "Do you agree to the final duel?<br>Or continue the game in normal format"
   "duel_bonus_information"                                                                                                      "A series of duels takes place to 3 wins. Before the duel, both players will receive 3 Retraining Books and 10k gold! Time before duel starts and preparation - 3 minutes. Or both players must press the Ready button and the duel will start immediately before 3 minutes expire! The player who wins 3 times (possible outcomes: 3-0, 3-1, 3-2) will be considered the winner. And the game ends! <br> Notes! When winning a death match, the player receives 1.5 times more rating (on loss - loses 2 times less)"
   
   "leave_from_game_is_banned"                                                                                                   "Punishment for leaving the game"
   "leave_from_game_is_banned_label"                                                                                             "If you leave the game or die from creeps before the 5th minute, hero selection will be blocked in the next game! <br>To remove the block, you will need to play with the hero that was initially given, and take at least top 4! <br>If a player leaves the game 3 times in a row without clearing the leave penalty, they receive the curse (cursed mark)! (the curse that is given for 322!). <br>The curse reduces outgoing damage to creeps and increases incoming damage to you! To remove the block you need to take at least top 4!"
