    "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_pirate_hat_custom_Description"                                                                     "<h1>Active: Dig</h1>Channels for %abilitychanneltime% sec. — creates a bounty rune at target point.\n\n<h1>Stats:</h1>+%bonus_attack_speed% attack speed<br>+%base_attack_speed%%% base attack speed<br>+%bonus_ms% movement speed"
  "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_pirate_hat_custom_Lore"                                                                              "A salty hat, carrying the curse of eternal luck."
    // Bonus stat labels intentionally omitted — values inline in Description's «Stats:».

    "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_panic_button_custom"                                                                               "Magic Lamp"
    "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_panic_button_custom_Description"                                                                   "<h1>Passive: Rejuvenate</h1>When owner's HP drops below %health_threshold%%%, applies a strong dispel and heals for %heal%%% of max HP. For %buff_duration% sec. the owner cannot deal or take damage.\n\n<h1>Stats:</h1>+%bonus_health% max HP"
    // Bonus stat labels intentionally omitted — values inline in Description's «Stats:».

    "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_skill_call_of_the_ancient_buff"                                                                        "Call of the Ancient"
    "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_skill_call_of_the_ancient_buff_Description"                                                            "This creature cannot be instantly killed by ability."

