//=================================================================================================================
// AncientArenaBeta_NEW_RUSSIAN_ADDON
//=================================================================================================================
  //=================================================================================================================
  // HEROES
  //=================================================================================================================
    //=================================================================================================================
    // STRENGTH
    //=================================================================================================================
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Alchemist
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom"                                                                     "Bounty Drop"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom_Description"                                                         "Channels for a short time, then creates a Bounty Rune at the target location. Picking up the rune grants gold based on the current game minute. Also passively increases gold received from all Bounty Runes."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom_Lore"                                                                "While the experiment with the mountain failed, Razzil easily turns smaller structures into jingling coin."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom_bounty_multiplier"                                                   "BOUNTY RUNE MULTIPLIER:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom_bounty_min_gold"                                                     "MIN GOLD:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom_bounty_max_gold"                                                     "MAX GOLD:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction"                                                             "Unstable Concoction"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Description"                                                 "The hero begins shaking a volatile concoction that can be thrown at an enemy hero. On impact, the flask explodes, stunning all enemies in the blast radius and dealing damage. The longer the concoction is shaken, the more damage it deals and the longer the stun. While holding the flask, the hero moves faster. Maximum effect is reached after %brew_time% sec., but if not thrown within %brew_explosion% seconds, it will explode in the hero's hands, affecting them as well."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Facet_alchemist_mixologist"                                  "This ability's cooldown is reduced by %chemical_rage_cooldown_reduction_pct%%% when its owner is affected by Chemical Rage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Lore"                                                        "Though turning a mountain into gold proved a failure, it yielded a volatile mixture with devastating potential."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_max_damage"                                                  "MAX DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_max_stun"                                                    "MAX STUN:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_move_speed"                                                  "%BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Note0"                                                       "While active, the ability is replaced with a throw. While shaking the mixture, the hero can move and act normally."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Note1"                                                       "A timer above the hero's head shows the time remaining until the explosion. Enemies can see this timer."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Note2"                                                       "This ability can be used to commit suicide."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Note3"                                                       "The flask cannot be disjointed. Its effect stops increasing after the throw."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_Note4"                                                       "The explosion damages both heroes and creeps."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_radius"                                                      "EXPLOSION RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_throw"                                                       "Unstable Concoction Throw"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_throw_Description"                                           "Throw it before it explodes!"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_alchemist_unstable_concoction_ability_note"                                                 "Can be used on creeps.<br>Works in area (AOE).<br>During activation hero is immune to effects."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_alchemist_chemical_rage_shard_description"                                                          "Adds new ability - Berserk Potion."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_drop_custom_Note0"                                                               "Gold formula: game minute x multiplier (min %bounty_min_gold%, max %bounty_max_gold%)."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_special_bonus_unique_cha_alchemist"                                                                 "Unused talent."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_alchemist_corrosive_weaponry_ability_note"                                                          "Ability passively increases debuff duration by %bonus_debuff_amplify%%%."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Axe
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom"                                                                           "Battle Hunger"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_Description"                                                               "Throws an enemy into a state of rage, dealing damage until they kill a target or until the duration expires. Damage increases based on owner's armor. If the victim turns away from the ability owner, their movement speed is reduced."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_Lore"                                                                      "Ordinary heroes cannot resist Mogul Khan's rage, and it cripples them until they take it out on someone."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_duration"                                                                  "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_slow"                                                                      "%MOVEMENT SLOW:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_damage_per_second"                                                         "DAMAGE PER SECOND:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_armor_multiplier"                                                          "ARMOR MULTIPLIER:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_abilitycastrange"                                                          "CAST RANGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_scepter_armor_change"                                                      "ARMOR CHANGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_scepter_description"                                                       "Reduces armor of ability victims and grants owner armor bonus for each victim. Ability works on multiple targets within Berserker's Call radius."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_battle_hunger_custom_debuff"                                                                   "Battle Hunger"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_battle_hunger_custom_debuff_Description"                                                       "Taking damage per second, movement speed reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_battle_hunger_custom_buff"                                                                     "Battle Hunger"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_battle_hunger_custom_buff_Description"                                                         "Armor increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_counter_helix_scepter_description"                                                              "Each proc applies a stacking effect on targets that reduces their attack damage against the ability owner. Owner's own attacks are also counted."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom"                                                                           "Culling Blade"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_Description"                                                               "Hero finds enemy's weak point and deals pure damage. If this ability kills an enemy hero, its cooldown resets, owner's armor permanently increases, and owner and nearby allies temporarily gain bonus movement speed."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_Note0"                                                                     "Kill with this ability cannot be prevented by other abilities: Shallow Grave, False Promise, Borrowed Time, Battle Trance."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_Lore"                                                                      "Like an embodiment of the fiercest battle, Mogul Khan brutally deals with those who dared to fight him."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_damage"                                                                    "DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_kill_threshold"                                                            "%HEALTH THRESHOLD FOR INSTANT KILL:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_speed_bonus"                                                               "%BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_atk_speed_bonus"                                                           "BONUS ATTACK SPEED:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_speed_aoe"                                                                 "SPEED RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_speed_duration"                                                            "SPEED DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_armor_per_stack"                                                           "ARMOR PER KILL:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_culling_blade_custom_ability_note"                                                              "Works on creeps. Adds 1 armor stack charge for killing a creep, once per round."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_culling_blade_custom_armor"                                                                    "Armor Loss from Culling Blade"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_culling_blade_custom_armor_Description"                                                        "+%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS% armor gained from Culling Blade ability."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_culling_blade_custom"                                                                          "Culling Blade"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_axe_culling_blade_custom_Description"                                                              "Axe's battle cry increased movement speed by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%% and attack speed by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_axe_battle_hunger_custom_Note0"                                                                     "This ability's effect is also removed if a building is destroyed."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Bristleback
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom"                                                               "Viscous Nasal Goo"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_Description"                                                   "Blows nose on victim, reducing their armor and movement speed. Ability effects stack, and duration refreshes with each application."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_shard_description"                                             "Increases maximum stacks by 2."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_Lore"                                                          "Rigwarl turns a cold caught in the snows to his advantage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_goo_duration"                                                  "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_base_armor"                                                    "BASE ARMOR REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_armor_per_stack"                                               "ARMOR REDUCTION PER STACK:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_base_move_slow"                                                "%BASE MOVEMENT SLOW:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_move_slow_per_stack"                                           "%SLOW PER STACK:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_stack_limit"                                                   "MAX STACKS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_radius_scepter"                                                "RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_stack_limit_scepter"                                           "MAX STACKS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_abilitycastrange"                                              "CAST RANGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom"                                                              "Viscous Nasal Goo"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_Description"                                                  "Loses %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS% armor and slowed by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_viscous_nasal_goo_custom_ability_note"                                                  "Instantly activates for all units within 900 radius."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom"                                                                     "Bristleback"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_abilitydraft_note"                                                   "If Quill Spray ability is not selected, hero will not cast it upon reaching damage threshold."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_Description"                                                         "Hero takes less damage from attacks from behind and sides. When taking %quill_release_threshold% damage from behind, casts Quill Spray of current level."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_Facet_bristleback_snot_rocket"                                       "Instead of quills, hero releases Viscous Nasal Goo of current level at all nearby enemies."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_Lore"                                                                "Sometimes it's useful to turn your back to the enemy in battle."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_Note0"                                                               "Hero's back is considered 70 degrees from the center of their back."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_Note1"                                                               "Hero's sides are considered 110 degrees from the center of their back."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_side_damage_reduction"                                               "%SIDE DAMAGE REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_back_damage_reduction"                                               "%BACK DAMAGE REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_quill_release_threshold"                                             "DAMAGE THRESHOLD:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_goo_radius"                                                          "GOO RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bristleback_bristleback_custom_scepter_description"                                                 "Allows casting this ability on a point. Hero turns their back to it and after 0.5 sec. releases 5 waves of Quill Spray in a cone-shaped area. Under this ability's effect, hero is slowed by 40% and cannot turn or attack, but can cast spells in any direction. Wave interval: 0.4 sec."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Centaur
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_centaur_double_edge_shard_description"                                                              "Ability slows victims and temporarily increases owner's strength for each enemy hero hit. Gaining a new stack refreshes duration of all stacks. Max stacks: 5"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_centaur_stampede_scepter_description"                                                               ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_special_bonus_unique_cha_centaur"                                                                   "+{s:bonus_return_damage_str}% return damage from strength"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_special_bonus_unique_cha_obsidian_destroyer"                                                     "+{s:value}% of current mana as movement speed"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_special_bonus_unique_cha_ogre_magi"                                                              "+{s:value} damage during Bloodlust"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_centaur_return_damage_block"                                                                        "%INCOMING DAMAGE REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_centaur_hoof_stomp_ability_note"                                                                    "Stun radius significantly increased!"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_centaur_return_ability_note"                                                                        "Passively reduces incoming damage!"
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Chaos Knight
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_reality_rift_shard_description"                                                        ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_chaos_bolt_ability_note"                                                               "15% chance that each attack activates ability on target, with 4.5 second cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_phantasm_ability_note"                                                                 "Damage to illusions significantly reduced"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_chaos_knight_fundamental_forging_Description"                                                       "When crafting a neutral item, your previous neutral is replaced in the choice pool with a random item from the next tier, and so cannot be re-picked. Does not affect tier 5."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Clockwerk
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_overclocking_ability_note"                                                               ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_hookshot_ability_note"                                                                   "Ability has reduced cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom"                                                                  "Battery Assault"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_Description"                                                      "Releases high-powered shrapnel at nearby units, dealing minor magical damage and briefly stunning them. Deals double damage to creeps."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_Lore"                                                             "Some of Rattletrap's devices don't work as intended, so in battle they can simply be detonated."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_Note0"                                                            "Continues to function even if hero is disabled."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_radius"                                                           "RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_duration"                                                         "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_interval"                                                         "INTERVAL:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_damage"                                                           "DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_rattletrap_battery_assault_custom_ability_note"                                                     "Ability applies to all targets in radius."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Dawnbreaker
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_fire_wreath_shard_description"                                                          ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom"                                                                      "Luminosity"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_Lore"                                                                 "Valora has weakened without the strengthening light of the Children of Light, but is still capable of fueling allied power, creating order from the chaos inherent in every battle."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_Description"                                                          "After %attack_count% attacks, hero is filled with power, causing the next attack to deal critical damage and heal all allied heroes within %heal_radius% for %allied_healing_pct%%% of damage. Healing from attacking a creep or neutral unit will be weaker."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_Note0"                                                                "Healing from this ability is considered lifesteal and is increased by corresponding sources."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_bonus_damage"                                                         "%CRITICAL DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_heal_pct"                                                             "%HEALING FROM HERO ATTACK:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_heal_from_creeps"                                                     "%HEALING REDUCTION FROM CREEP ATTACK:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_cooldown_reduction"                                                   "COOLDOWN REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_Facet_dawnbreaker_solar_charged"                                             "Making an attack with Luminosity effect, hero reduces cooldowns of all abilities and items."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Facet_dawnbreaker_solar_charged"                                                                            "Solar Charged"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Facet_dawnbreaker_solar_charged_Description"                                                                "Making an attack with Luminosity effect, hero reduces cooldowns of all abilities and items."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom"                                                                     "Luminosity"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_Description"                                                         "Preparing Luminosity attack"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_buff"                                                                "Luminosity Attack Effect"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_buff_Description"                                                    "Next attack will deal critical damage and heal allied heroes"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_fire_wreath_ability_note"                                                               "Increased swing radius and stun duration!"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_celestial_hammer_ability_note"                                                          "Fire trail radius increased"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_custom_ability_note"                                                         "Lifesteal from creeps increased!"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_solar_guardian_ability_note"                                                           ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom"                                                                "Scorched Earth"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_Description"                                                    "Deals periodic damage to surrounding enemies and increases movement speed."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Doom
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_shard_description"                                                              ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_ability_note"                                                                   "Rearm only refreshes 50% of ability"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_doom_scepter_description"                                                              "Ability affects victim's allies within 250 radius. Allows casting this ability on self, causing it to affect enemies around owner.<br><br><font color='#f00'>Ability radius cannot be increased by any effects or buffs.</font>"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom"                                                                         "Devour"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_Description"                                                             "Devours enemy or neutral creep, gaining their abilities and receiving bonus armor while they are digested. If auto-cast is disabled, abilities are not gained. Duration equals ability cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_shard_description"                                                       ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_Lore"                                                                    "Lucifer's gluttony and greed are inexhaustible."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_Note0"                                                                   "Devoured creep grants not only bonus gold, but also bounty for killing it."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_Note1"                                                                   "If used on a creep without abilities, previously gained abilities are retained."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_creep_level"                                                             "MAX CREEP LEVEL:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_bonus_gold"                                                              "BONUS GOLD:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_armor"                                                                   "BONUS ARMOR:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_devour_custom_ability_note"                                                            "Gold from ability can be obtained 3 times per round."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom"                                                                 "Scorched Earth"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_Description"                                                     "Covers ground around hero with flames, increasing movement speed and dealing damage to enemies."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_Lore"                                                            "The Fallen leaves terrible destruction in his wake—the flames that feed him spare no one."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_Note0"                                                           "Burning area moves with the hero."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_damage_per_second"                                               "DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_radius"                                                          "RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_bonus_movement_speed_pct"                                        "%BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_mana_cost"                                                       "MANA COST PER SEC:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_doom_bringer_scorched_earth_custom_ability_note"                                                    "Ability is now toggleable and drains mana per second"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_special_bonus_unique_cha_doom_bringer"                                                              "Unobstructed movement during Scorched Earth"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_doom_bringer_devour_custom"                                                                       "Digesting"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_doom_bringer_devour_custom_Description"                                                           "You will receive gold when the effect ends"

      //=================================================================================================================
      // Dragon Knight
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_tail_custom"                                                                   "Dragon Tail"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_tail_custom_Description"                                                       "Hero strikes enemy with shield within attack range, stunning them and dealing minor damage. In dragon form, this ability can be cast from %dragon_cast_range% distance."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_tail_custom_Lore"                                                              "Combining dragon abilities and knight skills, Davion becomes a dangerous opponent in melee combat."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_tail_custom_stun_duration"                                                     "STUN DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom"                                                             "Elder Dragon Form"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_Description"                                                 "Hero transforms into a mighty ancient dragon, moving faster, casting Dragon Tail from greater distance, and gaining special attack effects.\n<font color=\"#9acd32\">LEVEL 1: green dragon<br>Poison attack</font> poisons target for %corrosive_breath_duration% sec., dealing %corrosive_breath_damage% damage per second. Poison also affects buildings.\n<font color=\"#ff0000\">LEVEL 2: red dragon<br>Splash attack</font> deals %splash_damage_percent%%% damage to all enemies within %splash_radius% of target. Poisons all affected enemies.\n<font color=\"#87ceeb\">LEVEL 3: blue dragon<br>Freezing attack</font> slows all splash attack victims for %frost_duration% sec., reducing movement speed by %frost_bonus_movement_speed%%% and attack speed by %frost_bonus_attack_speed%. Poisons all affected enemies."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_shard_description"                                           "Gains Fireball ability while in dragon form."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_scepter_description"                                         "Increases ability level by 1. Adds fourth level with black dragon: magic resistance increased by 25%%, has free movement and enhanced slow, poison damage, and area damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_Lore"                                                        "The power of the ancient dragon, dormant within Davion, bursts forth, combining the might of a legendary knight with the power of a legendary dragon."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_Note0"                                                       "Damage from poison attacks is lethal."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_Note1"                                                       "Cooldown of some items depends on what attack type hero had when using them."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_duration"                                                    "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_bonus_movement_speed"                                        "BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_bonus_attack_range"                                          "BONUS ATTACK RANGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_frost"                                                      "Freezing Attack Slow"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_frost_Description"                                          "Movement speed reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%, attack speed reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_corrosive"                                                  "Poison Attack"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_corrosive_Description"                                      "Taking %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP% damage per second."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom"                                                            "Splash Attack"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_Description"                                                "Deals portion of damage to enemies in area around target."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_blood_custom"                                                                  "Dragon Blood"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_blood_custom_Description"                                                      "Dragon blood flowing in hero's veins enhances health regeneration and armor."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_blood_custom_bonus_health_regen"                                               "HEALTH REGENERATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_blood_custom_bonus_armor"                                                      "BONUS ARMOR:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_dragon_blood_custom_ability_note"                                                     "Stats significantly enhanced!"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_custom_ability_note"                                                "Elder Dragon Form changes hero's attack type to ranged."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dragon_knight_breathe_fire_ability_note"                                                          "Each attack has a 25% chance to instantly trigger this ability's effect. Cooldown — 1.5 seconds."
