        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_life_stealer_feast_custom"                                                                          "Feast"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_life_stealer_feast_custom_Description"                                                              "Adds to hero's attacks bonus damage and lifesteal based on enemy's maximum health."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_life_stealer_feast_custom_Lore"                                                                     "After escaping from Devarque's dungeon, N'aix began feeding on the flesh and bones of those unfortunate enough to meet him."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_life_stealer_feast_custom_Note0"                                                                    "Does not work on Roshan."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_life_stealer_feast_custom_Note1"                                                                    "Amount of health restored does not depend on damage dealt."
