        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lycan_summon_wolves_shard_description"                                                              ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lycan_shapeshift_custom"                                                                            "Shapeshift"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lycan_shapeshift_custom_Lore"                                                                       "Forever a slave to his lycanthropy, Banehallow has resigned himself to the curse and accepted his ferocity as a given."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lycan_shapeshift_custom_Description"                                                                "Hero assumes wolf form. During this ability's duration its owner and all creatures under his control move with increased speed, cannot be slowed, gain increased night vision and have %crit_chance%%% chance to perform critical attack dealing %crit_multiplier%%% damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lycan_shapeshift_custom_Note0"                                                                      "Hex does not affect your hero's movement speed."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lycan_shapeshift_custom_Note1"                                                                      "Under effect of this ability hero has smaller collision radius."
