        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_hunter_in_the_night_custom_ability_note"                                              "Grants bonus day and night."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_crippling_fear_ability_note"                                                          "Ability works identically day and night."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_darkness_custom"                                                                      "Dark Ascension"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_darkness_custom_Description"                                                          "Suppresses sunlight, creating impenetrable darkness and revealing hero's powers in full. He gains unobstructed vision, flight and bonus damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_darkness_custom_Lore"                                                                 "A pitiful sight: even strongest of warriors begin to fear the dark."
