        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sven_gods_strength_custom"                                                                          "God's Strength"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sven_gods_strength_custom_Description"                                                              "Hero concentrates his uncontrollable might, gaining damage bonus for %abilityduration% sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sven_gods_strength_custom_Lore"                                                                     "Endowed with strength that shattered Sacred Helm, rebellious knight is invincible in melee combat."
