        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom"                                                                     "Kraken Shell"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom_Description"                                                         "Thickens hero's hide, blocking portion of physical damage. When received damage reaches certain threshold, ability dispels all negative effects.\n\nEffect does not stack with items that block physical damage.\n\nDispel type: strong."
