        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom_Lore"                                                                "Stories of Claddish sailors tell of mighty sea monster that sank ships, paying no attention to spears piercing him and swords cutting him."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom_Note0"                                                               "When calculating received damage, only damage dealt by players is counted."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom_Note1"                                                               "Damage counter will reset if hero did not receive damage from players for last %damage_reset_interval% sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom_Note2"                                                               "Removes most negative effects not removed by other similar abilities."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tidehunter_kraken_shell_custom_ability_note"                                                        "Negative effects dispelling returned inside ability."
