        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua"                                                                               "Chakram"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_Description"                                                                   "Launches saw to specified location that spins, deals damage to enemies and slows their movement. Slow increases for every %slow_health_percentage%%% of victim's missing health. Saw deals pure damage and cuts all trees in its path. While ability is active, its owner cannot attack and gradually loses mana."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_Lore"                                                                          "Universal weapon for flora annihilation"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shredder_chakram_lua_Note0"                                                                         "Saw will return to owner if he runs out of mana or if he moves away more than %break_distance%."
