        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_flesh_golem_custom_Description"                                                             "Hero transforms into terrifying flesh golem. Golem has increased strength, and his attacks slow victims and increase damage they take."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_flesh_golem_custom_Lore"                                                                    "Flesh of fresh corpses amplifies death herald's plague."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_flesh_golem_custom_duration"                                                                "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_undying_flesh_golem_custom_slow"                                                                    "%SLOW:"
