        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_special_bonus_unique_wraith_king_5"                                                                 "x3 Vampiric Spirit skeleton health"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skeleton_king_hellfire_blast_crit_mult"                                                            "%CRITICAL DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skeleton_king_hellfire_blast_Description"                                                          "The hero scorches the target with spectral fire, stunning it and dealing damage. After the stun, the target takes damage over time and is slowed.<br><br><span class='GameplayValues GameplayVariable'>Passive: Mortal Strike</span><br>The hero periodically deals bonus critical damage with attacks."
