        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_hunter_jinada"                                                                              "Jinada"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_hunter_jinada_ability_note"                                                                 "Does not steal gold from heroes."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_hunter_jinada_Description"                                                                  "The hero carefully plans the next attack, dealing bonus damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_hunter_jinada_gold_steal"                                                                   ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bounty_hunter_jinada_Lore"                                                                         "Gondar's vast experience ensures he never leaves a deal empty-handed."
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Broodmother
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_spin_web_scepter_description"                                                           ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_silken_bola_shard_description"                                                          ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_shard_Description"                                                    "Increases duration. While this ability is active, bonus damage increases by 12 every %shard_damage_tick_interval% sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom"                                                               "Insatiable Hunger"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_Description"                                                   "Insatiable thirst for nutritious juices increases hero's damage and grants lifesteal.<br><br>Bonus damage <font color='#f00'>Disabled by break</font>"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_shard_Description"                                             "Increases duration. While this ability is active, bonus damage increases by %shard_damage_per_tick%%% every %shard_damage_tick_interval% sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_Lore"                                                          "Most of her victims spider wraps in silk cocoons and leaves to feed brood, but she also likes to feast on lost heroes."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_Note0"                                                         "Fully stacks with other lifesteal sources."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_bonus_damage"                                                  "%BONUS TO BASE ATTACK DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_lifesteal_pct"                                                 "%LIFESTEAL:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_duration"                                                      "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_shard_spiderling_duration"                                     "DURATION ON SPIDERLINGS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_shard_creep_pct"                                               "%CHANCE TO INFECT CREEP:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_shard_hero_pct"                                                "%CHANCE TO INFECT HERO:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_damage_pct"                                                    "%BONUS DAMAGE FROM TARGET'S MAX HEALTH:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_insatiable_hunger_custom_ability_note"                                                  "Deals increased damage based on target's maximum health.<br>Proc interval: 0.15 sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_silken_bola"                                                                             "Silken Bola"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_silken_bola_Description"                                                                 "Ensnares an enemy unit in webbing, dealing damage. The target misses attacks and moves slower, and any attack against it deals bonus magic damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_silken_bola_damage"                                                                      "DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_broodmother_silken_bola_miss_chance"                                                                 "MISS CHANCE:"
