        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_kez_kazurai_katana_custom"                                                                          "Kazurai Katana"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_kez_kazurai_katana_custom_Lore"                                                                     "To succeed in fight against Empire and its guardians, kazurai had to become proficient in war of attrition."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_kez_kazurai_katana_custom_Description"                                                              "When hero uses katana, his attacks and abilities apply stacking effect on enemies that gradually deals portion of attack damage. This effect also reduces enemy health regeneration. Health regeneration reduction effect doesn't stack."
