        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_kez_kazurai_katana_custom_shard_description"                                                        "Ability can be cast so hero pierces enemy with katana, briefly stunning him and himself, after which all effects from this ability are removed from victim, instantly dealing all remaining damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_kez_kazurai_katana_custom_stun_duration"                                                            "STUN DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_kez_kazurai_katana_custom_bleed_as_rupture_pct"                                                     "%DAMAGE FROM EFFECTS:"
