        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lone_druid_true_form_custom_Description"                                                            "Hero's knowledge allows him to turn into enraged bear that fights in melee. In this form he has increased health and armor, as well as enhanced Entangling Claws and Demolish abilities."
