        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_rip_tide_lua_Description"                                                                "After making total of %hits% attacks, hero and all his illusions drench nearby enemies with powerful water wave, dealing them damage and reducing their armor for %duration% sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_rip_tide_lua_Lore"                                                                       "Flow from deepest depths sweeps away siren's opponents' defense."
