        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_shard_description"                                                     "Increases duration. Ability restores allies within radius 5% of their maximum health each second."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom"                                                                "Song of the Siren"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom_Description"                                                    "All enemies in certain area around hero fall into magical sleep in which they cannot do anything. Recasting ability will end it prematurely."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom_shard_description"                                              "Ability restores allies within radius %heal_pct%%% of their maximum health each second."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom_Lore"                                                           "Powerful voice of Slithice charms hordes of opponents while kinfolk rush to her aid."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom_Note0"                                                          "Enemies under this ability effect are invulnerable and cannot take damage from any source."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom_Note1"                                                          "Doesn't pierce debuff immunity."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_song_of_the_siren_custom_Note2"                                                          "Spell area of effect moves with you, so creatures at sufficient distance will wake up."
