        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_riki_poison_dart_debuff_Description"	"Movement speed slowed."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_backstab_custom_Description"                                                                   "Hero goes into shadows, becoming invisible. Each his attack deals bonus damage based on agility and doubled on non-hero creatures. When attacking invisibility fades."
