        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_backstab_custom_Lore"                                                                          "Riki is following you."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_tricks_of_the_trade_custom"                                                                    "Tricks of the Trade"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_tricks_of_the_trade_custom_Description"                                                        "CHANNELING — hero disappears from our world and periodically backstabs random enemy in area of effect."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_tricks_of_the_trade_custom_scepter_description"                                                "Increases cast range and attack count"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_tricks_of_the_trade_custom_Lore"                                                               "Stealthy assassin believes all means are good in battle and doesn't hesitate to backstab."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_tricks_of_the_trade_custom_Note0"                                                              "Ability can be interrupted by movement command."
