      //=================================================================================================================
      // Shadow Fiend
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua"                                                                  "Requiem of Souls"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Description"                                                      "Hero releases collected souls in waves of demonic energy. Creatures near him can take damage from multiple waves. For each hit wave victim receives %requiem_slow_duration% sec. slow, magic resistance reduction and fear (but no more than %requiem_slow_duration% sec.). Creates one energy wave per each soul captured with Necromastery.<br><br>If hero dies, this ability will trigger automatically regardless of its readiness."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_scepter_description"                                              "Reduces cooldown. Increases soul count to 23. Makes weakened waves of this ability return to hero, healing him for amount of damage dealt on return path."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_ability_note"                                                     "Doesn't require <font color='#B694FF'>Necromastery</font> ability. Releases 18 souls (23 souls with Scepter)."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_abilitycastpoint"                                                 "CAST DELAY:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_reduction_ms"                                             "%MOVEMENT SLOW:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_reduction_damage"                                         "%DAMAGE REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_damage_pct_scepter"                                       "%DAMAGE ON RETURN:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_requiem_heal_pct_scepter"                                         "%HEALING ON RETURN:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Lore"                                                             "Imprisoned souls of those who fell in past battles gain freedom to vengefully pursue their former allies."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note0"                                                            "Creates up to 18 damage waves (23 with Aghanim's Scepter)."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_shadow_fiend_requiem_of_souls_lua_Note1"                                                            "Slow pierces magic immunity."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nevermore_dark_lord_shard_description"                                                              ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nevermore_shadowraze1_custom"                                                                       "Shadowraze"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nevermore_shadowraze1_custom_Description"                                                           "Hero devastates patch of ground right in front of him, dealing damage to all enemies in area. Applies stacking effect on victim that with each Shadowraze hit increases damage from it and slows victim's movement."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nevermore_shadowraze1_custom_Lore"                                                                  "Signature method of soul collecting."
