        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_troll_warlord_berserkers_rage_ability_note"                                                         "Attack interval set to 1.1 seconds. Hero gains bonus armor: 5/7/10/14. When activating ability status resistance increases by 25%, and attack type changes to melee."
