        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_custom_shard_description"                                              "Projectile bounces to another enemy (prioritizing heroes) within current ability cast range."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_custom_Lore"                                                           "Simplest Skywrath technique — magic projectile — is Shendelzare's main instrument of revenge."
