      //=================================================================================================================
      // Weaver
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_custom"                                                        "Geminate Attack"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_custom_Description"                                            "Allows hero to make multiple attacks instead of one. <font color='#70EA72'>Bonus attack works on both main target and other enemies.</font>"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_custom_Lore"                                                   "To some extent Skitskurr exists outside time concept, so his actions are seen — and felt — not just once."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_custom_Note0"                                                  "Hero attacks second time quarter second after first attack regardless of distance to target."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_frostivus2018_weaver_geminate_attack_custom_tooltip_attack"                                         "BONUS ATTACK COUNT:"
