        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_special_bonus_unique_ancient_apparition_6"                                                          "Cold Feet deals 2x damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom"                                                                "Cold Feet"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom_Description"                                                    "Applies frost spell on enemy, causing them to take periodic damage. Effect dispels if target moves far enough from ability cast point. Otherwise after 4 seconds target will be stunned and frozen in place."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom_Lore"                                                           "Kaldr's presence turns surroundings into frost void, threatening to lock them in ice prison forever."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom_Note0"                                                          "Deals damage every half second. Cold Feet deals 2x damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom_damage"                                                         "DAMAGE PER SECOND:"
