        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom_Description"                                                   "Taking damage over time and will be immobilized if doesn't retreat"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_ancient_apparition_cold_feet_custom_stunned"                                                       "Frozen"
