        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_innate_disabled_placeholder_Description"                                                           "Innate ability is temporarily disabled. It is being reworked and will be added soon."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lone_druid_starter_innate"                                                                         "Call of Yama Raskav"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lone_druid_starter_innate_Description"                                                             "Sylla, the last of his druidic order, is forever bound to the ancient Yama Raskav jungle. The wilderness answers its keeper with <font color='#cc7733'>entangling vines</font> — a gift that can be neither forgotten nor passed on."

