        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_custom"                                                                      "Ink Swell"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_custom_Description"                                                          "Hero covers self or ally with ink that increases movement speed and deals damage to nearby enemies. After %buff_duration% sec. ink splashes, stunning enemies and dealing them damage. Stun duration and splash damage depend on how long ink was affecting enemy heroes."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_custom_shard_description"                                                    "Ability deals %shard_bonus_damage_pct%%% more damage. %shard_heal_pct%%% of damage dealt heals target, and at end applies strong dispel to target.<br><br>DISPEL TYPE: strong"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_custom_Lore"                                                                 "Now that ink absorption no longer threatens ascended one, their power is always at his disposal."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_custom_buff_duration"                                                        "DELAY BEFORE ACTIVATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_custom_movespeed_bonus_pct"                                                  "%BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED:"
