        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua"                                                                              "Cold Snap"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_Description"                                                                  "Draws heat from enemy for time. Enemy takes damage and will be briefly frozen. Subsequent damage taken in this state will freeze enemy again and deal additional damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_cold_snap_lua_Lore"                                                                         "Sadron's protracted shiver."
