        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_chaos_meteor_lua_Description"                                                               "Hero brings down from heavens burning meteor that after landing rolls forward. Meteor touch deals damage and briefly engulfs victim in fire dealing periodic damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_chaos_meteor_lua_Lore"                                                                      "Tarak's descent of fire."
