        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_sun_strike_lua_scepter_description"                                                         "Double tap on Sun Strike creates 2 beams visible to enemies within 90-180 radius from each enemy hero. Cooldown: 90 seconds."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_invoker_deafening_blast_lua"                                                                        "Deafening Blast"
