        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_ice_lua"                                                                              "Liquid Frost"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_jakiro_liquid_ice_lua_Description"                                                                  "Hero coats their attack with freezing liquid, chilling the target and all enemies around it. Victims are briefly stunned, slowed, and take periodic magic damage based on their max health."
