        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_custom"                                                             "Spirit Form"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_custom_Description"                                                 "Transforms hero's body into pure light, granting increased movement speed and spell cast range."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_custom_Lore"                                                        "Ezalor reveals his true essence with flash of light."
