        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_custom_spell_lifesteal"                                             "%SPELL LIFESTEAL:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_custom"                                                            "Spirit Form"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_keeper_of_the_light_spirit_form_custom_Description"                                                "Ability becomes toggle. When activated hero gains ability to pass through obstacles. Effect persists until toggled off again."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_illuminate_custom"                                                              "Illuminate"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_illuminate_custom_Description"                                                  "CHANNELED — creates wave of bright energy in front, gradually gaining power. Released wave deals damage and temporarily reveals fog of war. Longer wave was channeled, more damage it deals."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_illuminate_custom_shard_description"                                            "Increases healing from Illuminate."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_illuminate_custom_Lore"                                                         "Light concealed in Ezalor manifests in amazing form."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_illuminate_custom_Note0"                                                        "While casting this spell you gain increased vision."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_keeper_of_the_light_illuminate_custom_total_damage"                                                 "MAX DAMAGE:"
