        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_death_charge"                                                                               "Innate Ability"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_death_charge_Description"                                                                   "Innate ability is temporarily disabled. It is being reworked and will be added soon."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_sinister_gaze_scepter_description"                                                             "Ability affects all enemies in selected area with 400 radius. During its use other abilities can be cast."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom"                                                                            "Chain Frost"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_Description"                                                                "Creates ice ball that bounces from opponents up to %jumps% times, slowing them and dealing damage that increases with each bounce."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_Lore"                                                                       "Ethreain's ice ball is universally considered pinnacle of ice magic mastery, striking fear into anyone who dares stand in sorcerer's path."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_Note0"                                                                      "This ability's projectile cannot be disjointed."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_Note1"                                                                      "Projectile flies at %projectile_speed% speed."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_Note2"                                                                      "Doesn't work on zombies summoned by Undying's Tombstone."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_damage"                                                                     "DAMAGE PER BOUNCE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_jumps"                                                                      "BOUNCES:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lich_chain_frost_custom_jump_range"                                                                 "BOUNCE RADIUS:"
