        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lion_finger_of_death_custom"                                                                        "Finger of Death"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lion_finger_of_death_custom_ability_note"                                                           "Works on creeps. Adds 1 stack of ability damage increase per creep kill, once per round. With Aghanim's Scepter cooldown: 80 / 50 / 20 sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lion_finger_of_death_custom_Description"                                                            "Rips enemy creature, trying to turn it inside out. Deals large damage that increases with each enemy killed by this ability."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_lion_finger_of_death_custom_scepter_description"                                                    "Increases damage and reduces cooldown. Ability affects creatures in small area."
