        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_respawn_time_custom"                                                      "Reaper's Scythe Creep"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_respawn_time_custom_Description"                                          "Kills permanently increased health regen by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_HEALTH_REGEN_CONSTANT%, and mana regen by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MANA_REGEN_CONSTANT%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_sadist_custom"                                                                            "Ghost Shroud"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_sadist_custom_Description"                                                                "Hero opens connection with world of deceased, slowing enemies around. In this form they cannot attack, take increased magical damage, but are protected from physical attacks and restore health and mana faster."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_sadist_custom_scepter_description"                                                        "Reduces cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_sadist_custom_Lore"                                                                       "With souls of his victims Rotund'jere blurs line between life and death."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_sadist_custom_duration"                                                                   "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_sadist_custom_heal_bonus"                                                                 "%REGEN AMPLIFICATION:"
