        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_multicast_lua_aghanim_description"                                                        "Adds the Unrefined Fireblast ability. Multicast can be used on allies to give them chance to multicast for some time. Multicast chance on ultimates is decreased by 50%"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_multicast_lua_ability_note"                                                               "This ability is incompatible with other abilities. Hold Alt for detailed information."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_multicast_lua"                                                                                     "Multicast"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_fireblast_custom"                                                                         "Fireblast"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_fireblast_custom_Description"                                                             "Hits enemy with fire wave, dealing damage and stunning target."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_fireblast_custom_Lore"                                                                    "Ogres are easy to entertain: they amuse themselves for hours playing with fire."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ogre_magi_fireblast_custom_Note0"                                                                   "With multicast stuns are dealt at %multicast_delay% sec. interval."
