        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_oracle_false_promise_custom"                                                                        "False Promise"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_oracle_false_promise_custom_Description"                                                            "Delays ally's fate, postponing any healing and damage taken until end of this ability. Any healing during this ability is amplified. Cast removes most negative effects from target.\n\nDISPEL TYPE: strong"
