        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua"                                                              "Sanity's Eclipse"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_Description"                                                  "Releases psychic charge that affects enemies based on difference between your mana and target's mana. Sanity's Eclipse can hit units trapped in Astral Imprisonment."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_Lore"                                                         "When Outworld crystal shatters, catastrophic energy is released, and reflection of this power is felt interdimensionally."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_base_damage"                                                  "BASE DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_damage_multiplier"                                            "MANA DIFFERENCE MULTIPLIER:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_radius"                                                       "RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_cast_range"                                                   "CAST RANGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_imba_essence_aura_buff"                                                                            "Essence Aura"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_imba_essence_aura_buff_Description"                                                                "Using abilities can restore portion of mana."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_astral_imprisonment_scepter_description"                                         ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_astral_imprisonment_shard_description"                                           "Increases mana pool steal. Allows allies under this ability effect to move at 60% speed. They cannot perform other actions and are visible to enemies, but cannot be targeted."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_astral_imprisonment_ability_note"                                               ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse_lua_ability_note"                                                 "Ability has reduced cooldown.<br><br>Can deal damage to creeps and neutral units."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_obsidian_destroyer_arcane_orb_ability_note"                                                         "If you have Arcane orb you cannot get Split shot!"
      //=================================================================================================================
      // Puck
      //=================================================================================================================
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom"                                                                            "Phase Shift"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_Description"                                                                "CHANNELED — hero briefly shifts to another dimension, protecting from any harm."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_shard_description"                                                          "Upon casting this ability hero attacks all enemies within attack range + %shard_attack_range_bonus%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_Lore"                                                                       "With mischievous smirk, faerie dragon returns with flash to other dimension native to it."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_Note0"                                                                      "Hero under this ability effect cannot be walked through."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_Note1"                                                                      "Any command will end this ability effect."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_Note2"                                                                      "Hero is invulnerable under this ability."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_phase_shift_custom_duration"                                                                   "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_puck_phase_shift_custom"                                                                           "Phase Shift"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_puck_phase_shift_custom_Description"                                                               "Temporarily beyond existence"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_dream_coil_custom"                                                                             "Dream Coil"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_dream_coil_custom_Description"                                                                 "Latches enemy heroes with unstable magical coil, applying leash effect and dealing damage. If enemy moves too far from coil center, it breaks, stunning them and dealing additional damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_dream_coil_custom_scepter_Description"                                                         "Ability owner attacks all enemies under its effect at 0.5 interval. If enemy breaks coil, attacks stop only after stun ends."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_puck_dream_coil_custom_Lore"                                                                        "Faerie dragon sows confusion in enemy ranks, making them realize their mortality."
