        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_pugna_nether_blast_delay"                                                                  "DELAY:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_pugna_nether_blast_Description"                                                            "A blast of astral energy that damages enemies and structures in the area.<br><br>The blast repeats immediately after the first one ends."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_ability_pugna_nether_blast_Lore"                                                                   "The Arts of Oblivion include a stunning blast of emerald flames from the Nether Reaches."
