        "npc_dota_pugna_ward_winter_2018"                                                                                         "Saprophytic Ward"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_pugna_ward_winter_2018_effect"                                                                     "Saprophytic Ward"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_scepter_description"                                                               "Reduces cooldown by 3.5 sec. Casting this ability on enemy hero each second reduces their spell damage by 8% (maximum — 75%), while increasing owner's spell damage up to 100%. When cast through Nether Ward totem damage change rate is 4%. This effect lasts 8 sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom"                                                                            "Life Drain"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_Description"                                                                "CHANNELED — when cast on enemy grants vision of them and drains their life force, replenishing hero's health. After full heal this ability replenishes hero's mana.\n\nWhen cast on ally hero transfers their health to them."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_Lore"                                                                       "Truly, even lord of Oblivion cannot fathom his might."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_Note0"                                                                      "Health gained depends on damage dealt."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_Note1"                                                                      "Instantly destroys illusions."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_health_drain"                                                               "HEALTH PER SECOND:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_abilitycastrange"                                                           "CAST RANGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_abilitychanneltime"                                                         "MAX DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_radius"                                                                     "EFFECT RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_pugna_life_drain_custom_scepter_description"                                                        "Reduces cooldown by 3.5 sec. Casting this ability on enemy hero each second reduces their spell damage by 8% (maximum — 75%), while increasing owner's spell damage up to 100%. This effect lasts 8 sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_pugna_life_drain_custom"                                                                           "Life Drain"
