        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skywrath_mage_arcane_bolt_custom_Description"                                                       "Hero fires slow magical energy charge at enemy that deals damage based on ability owner's intelligence. Hit applies effect to victim granting ability owner bonus spell lifesteal against them."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skywrath_mage_arcane_bolt_custom_Lore"                                                              "Among endless intrigues of Ghastly Eyrie only clever and calm can hope to survive."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skywrath_mage_arcane_bolt_custom_Note0"                                                             "Projectile moves at slow speed of 500, grants 325 vision and reveals area around target for 3.34 seconds after hit."
