        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_thundergods_vengeance_custom_Description"                                                      "Strikes all enemy heroes with lightning regardless of their location. Ability also reveals invisible enemy creatures around each struck opponent. If enemy hero is invisible, they won't take damage but invisibility will still be revealed."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_thundergods_vengeance_custom_Lore"                                                             "Lord of heavens crushes all who oppose him, regardless of whether they are near or far."
