        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_lightning_hands_custom"                                                                        "Lightning Hands"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_lightning_hands_custom_Description"                                                            "Increases hero attack range. They create Arc Lightning bolts dealing portion of ability damage."
