        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_lightning_bolt_custom"                                                                         "Lightning Bolt"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_lightning_bolt_custom_Description"                                                             "Lightning strike deals damage to enemy and briefly stuns them. Within %sight_radius_night% radius around target temporarily grants unobstructed vision and reveals invisibility. Ability can be cast on ground — then affects everyone in %spread_aoe% radius. Deals %creep_damage_bonus_pct%%% more damage to creeps."
