        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_cloud_custom_lore"                                                                             "Where thunder god rages, clouds soon gather."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_lightning_bolt_custom_ability_note"                                                            "Works on point and deals damage to all creatures in 400 radius. Deals additional 8% of target max health"
