        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_heavenly_jump_custom"                                                                          "Heavenly Jump"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_zuus_heavenly_jump_custom_Description"                                                              "Hero performs divine leap forward during which they shock nearest visible enemy (prioritizing heroes), dealing damage and slowing their movement and attack. Ability grants unobstructed vision in 900 radius around owner for 3 seconds."
