        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom"                                                                       "Borrowed Time"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_Description"                                                           "Converts all received damage into healing. Casting removes most negative effects. If ability is ready, triggers automatically when owner's health drops below %hp_threshold%.\n\nDISPEL TYPE: strong"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_Lore"                                                                  "This power, most unnatural of all gifts from Avernus font, defies mortal understanding. What should wound — heals, what should kill — grants fresh strength."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_hp_threshold"                                                          "HEALTH THRESHOLD:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_duration"                                                              "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_duration_scepter"                                                      "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_redirect_range_scepter"                                                "EFFECT RADIUS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_ally_threshold_scepter"                                                "DAMAGE FOR HEALING:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_scepter_description"                                                   "Increases duration by 1.5 seconds."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_Note0"                                                                 "This ability can be cast if hero is disabled but not silenced. Automatic trigger works even under silence."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_Note1"                                                                 "Shield doesn't block damage during Borrowed Time."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_ability_note"                                                          ""
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_buff"                                                                 "Borrowed Time"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_abaddon_borrowed_time_custom_buff_Description"                                                     "Damage received heals instead of harming."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_aphotic_shield_ability_note"                                                                "Triggers passively upon taking 400 damage, with 7 second cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_abaddon_death_coil_ability_note"                                                                    "Ability affects all enemies in 300 radius and triggers automatically on attack with 15% chance."
