        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_arc_warden_tempest_double_lua"                                                                      "Tempest Double"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_arc_warden_tempest_double_lua_Description"                                                          "Concentrating fragments into single entity, hero creates their electric copy that can use abilities and all items except many consumables and those lost on death. Copy has separate cooldowns for abilities and items. Killing copy grants enemy gold. Copy loses itself if too far from creator and deals less damage with attacks."
