        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_Description"                                                       "Converts creep into three controlled fragments of hero — eidolons. They split after several attacks, fully restoring health."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_Lore"                                                              "Primordial can draw entities from other dimensions, creating trinity of dark eidolons in material world."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_Note0"                                                             "Converting enemy into eidolon grants gold and experience for kill."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_Note1"                                                             "Converted allied creatures count as denied."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_Note2"                                                             "Cannot target ancient creeps or neutral creeps above level 4."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_Note3"                                                             "Cannot target flagbearer creeps."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_split_attack_count"                                                "ATTACKS TO SPLIT:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_demonic_conversion_custom_spawn_count"                                                       "EIDOLON COUNT:"
