        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_malefice_custom"                                                                             "Malefice"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_malefice_custom_Description"                                                                 "Concentrates hero energy on target, causing them to take damage and stun every %tick_rate% sec."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_malefice_custom_Lore"                                                                        "Alien gravitational forces compress very essence of enemies, binding all their movement."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_malefice_custom_stun_duration"                                                               "STUN DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_malefice_custom_damage"                                                                      "DAMAGE PER INSTANCE:"
