        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_black_hole_ability_note"                                                                     "Ability has reduced cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_enigma_midnight_pulse_custom_ability_note"                                                          "Damage from max health. Doesn't work on Roshan and Godhj."
