        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom"                                                                "Spiked Carapace"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom_Description"                                                    "Completely blocks damage from attack or ability, reflecting damage once and stunning each attacker. Doesn't break Vendetta invisibility.\n\nIf hero is under Burrow effect, this ability instantly stuns all nearby enemies."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom_Lore"                                                           "Though scarab carapace itself is quite thin, it's reliably protected by razor-sharp retractable spikes."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom_Note0"                                                          "Deals damage reduced by your resistance stats."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom_Note1"                                                          "Only works on player-controlled units."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom_Note2"                                                          "Reflected damage has same type as dealt."
