        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_nyx_assassin_spiked_carapace_custom_Description"                                                   "Next damage dealt by player will be reflected, stunning and damaging attacker."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_nyx_assassin_burrow_ability_note"                                                                  ""
