        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_snapfire_gobble_up_custom"                        "Gobble Up"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_snapfire_gobble_up_custom_Description"            "Snapfire gobbles up allied creep or hero, granting protection and charging with fire energy. Gobbled ally can be spit out at target location, dealing damage and stunning enemies in landing area."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_snapfire_gobble_up_custom_creep_duration"         "DURATION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_snapfire_gobble_up_custom_damage_per_second"      "DAMAGE PER SECOND:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_snapfire_gobble_up_custom_Aghanim_Description"    "Grants Gobble Up ability that allows gobbling allied creeps or heroes. Gobbled allies can be spit out at target location, dealing damage and stunning enemies in landing area."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_snapfire_gobble_up_custom_Note0"                  "Creeps always die when gobbled."
