        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom"                                                                          "Dispersion"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom_shard_description"                                                        "Allows activating this ability to increase reflected damage by %activation_bonus_pct%%%. Duration: %activation_duration% sec. Cooldown: %activation_cooldown% sec. Mana cost: %activation_manacost%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom_Description"                                                              "Damage dealt to ability owner reflects to enemies without harming owner. Effect weakens with distance."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom_Lore"                                                                     "Difficult task faces Mercurial's enemies — killing shadow with sword and magic."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom_Note0"                                                                    "Reflected damage not dealt to ability owner."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom_Note1"                                                                    "Illusions don't have this ability."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_dispersion_custom_Note2"                                                                    "Reflected damage returns unreduced and has same type as dealt."
