        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom"                                                                            "Desolate"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_Description"                                                                "Each attack deals bonus damage, if target is creep damage multiplied by %creep_multiplier%."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_Lore"                                                                       "Often warriors find themselves alone with Mercurial's image. But whether it's real — that's question that seals their fate."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_Note0"                                                                      "Damage dealt before attack completes."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_Note1"                                                                      "Works on illusions."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_bonus_damage"                                                               "BONUS DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_attack_speed"                                                               "BONUS ATTACK SPEED:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_spectral_dagger_ability_note"                                                               "Passively procs on taking 300 damage with 1.5 sec cooldown."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spectre_desolate_custom_ability_note"                                                               "Grants bonus attack speed. Creep damage increased!"
