        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_summon_familiars_ability_note"                                                               "<font color='#B694FF'>Summon power</font> affects this ability with <font color='#B694FF'>120% effectiveness</font>."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua"                                                                      "Gravekeeper's Cloak"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Description"                                                          "Visage creates multilayer barrier that protects from damage.<br><br>Layers can be destroyed by heroes and creeps. Heroes destroy %hero_multiplier% layers and creeps destroy one. Layers need time to recover."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_shard_Description"                                                    "Grants Visage ability to use Stone Form. Restores up to 35% health. Cooldown: 60. Mana cost: 125."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Lore"                                                                 "Visage's tough scales possess properties of both wraith and stone, making him nearly impervious to blades and magical attacks."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Note0"                                                                "Each time Visage takes damage exceeding minimum damage that wasn't self-inflicted, layer disappears."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Note1"                                                                "Familiars within %radius% radius of Visage receive current damage reduction from Gravekeeper's Cloak."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_damage_reduction"                                                     "%DAMAGE REDUCTION PER LAYER:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_max_layers"                                                           "MAX LAYERS:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_recovery_time"                                                        "LAYER RECOVERY TIME:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_minimum_damage"                                                       "MINIMUM DAMAGE:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_max_damage_reduction"                                                 "%MAX DAMAGE REDUCTION:"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua"                                                                     "Gravekeeper's Cloak"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_lua_Description"                                                         "Each charge reduces incoming damage."
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_secondary_lua"                                                           "Gravekeeper's Cloak"
        "DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_visage_gravekeepers_cloak_secondary_lua_Description"                                               "Takes less damage."
