      "VOTES_LIST_MULT_EXP"                                                                                                               "Experience multiplier"
      "VOTES_LIST_ROUND_WHEN_CAN_SUMMON_CREEPS"                                                                                           "Starting round for summoning creeps"
      "VOTES_LIST_ROUND_WHEN_QUEUE_START"                                                                                                "Starting round for queue game"
      "CUSTOM_VOTES_CAT_PLAYER"                                                                                                          "Player"
      "CUSTOM_VOTES_CAT_ABILITIES"                                                                                                       "Abilities"
      "CUSTOM_VOTES_CAT_CREEPS"                                                                                                          "Creeps"
      "CUSTOM_VOTES_CAT_ROUNDS"                                                                                                          "Rounds"
      "CUSTOM_VOTES_CAT_SKILLS"                                                                                                          "Skills"
      "VOTES_Result_Header"                                                                                                           "Voting complete"
		  "VOTES_Result_Header_desc"                                                                                                      "Following option selected"
      "VOTES_Result_mini_Header"                                                                                                     "Voting Results"
      "VOTES_CONFIRM_HEADER"                                                                                                          "Confirm vote"
      "VOTES_CONFIRM_SELECTED"                                                                                                        "Selected option"
      "VOTES_CONFIRM_YES"                                                                                                             "Confirm"
      "VOTES_CONFIRM_NO"                                                                                                              "Cancel"
      "ROUNDS_VoteGameModeDesc"                                             "Currently you need to choose game mode for this round.<br><br>Winning any mode grants winner effect - it increases all damage by 10% per victory.<br>Effect loses 1 charge if you lose first in any mode or lose aegis charge."
      "VOTES_LIST_SETTINGS_STATE_tooltip"                                   "This mode allows configuring game difficulty or creating custom parameters. Left mode selected by default."
      "VOTES_LIST_DIFFICULT_SELECTION_tooltip"                              "This mode allows maximum customization of lobby settings. Recommended only for experienced players"
      "VOTES_LIST_BANS_DURATION_tooltip"                                    "Banning stage duration"
      "VOTES_LIST_CREEP_BONUS_ARMOR_tooltip"                                "Multiplier of creep armor growth per wave after round 50.<br><br>Lower values make late rounds easier, higher values make them noticeably harder and favor physical damage builds."
      "VOTES_LIST_CREEP_BONUS_MAGIC_RESISTANCE_tooltip"                     "Multiplier of creep magic resistance growth per wave after round 50.<br><br>Affects magical damage efficiency in the late game: the higher the value, the less viable pure magic builds become."
      "VOTES_LIST_INIT_LIFES_tooltip"                                       "How many duels your team can lose before being eliminated.<br><br>Each life equals one aegis charge. One life makes the game instantly lethal, three gives more room for mistakes and extends matches."
      "VOTES_LIST_SSS_COUNT_FIRST_tooltip"                                  "Number of guaranteed SSS-tier abilities in the first ability pick (out of 8 options).<br><br>SSS abilities are the top rarity — the more in the first pick, the stronger your early potential.<br>0 means relying on common abilities scaling, 3 almost guarantees a powerful first skill."
      "VOTES_LIST_INIT_REROLLS_tooltip"                                     "Starting amount of free rerolls during the hero pick stage.<br><br>A reroll refreshes the random pool of available heroes. More rerolls — more chances to build a comfortable pick and the desired synergy."
      "VOTES_LIST_INIT_SMOKES_tooltip"                                      "Starting smoke count"
      "VOTES_LIST_PICKS_DURATION_tooltip"                                   "Time to pick hero"
      "VOTES_LIST_FIRST_ABILITY_IS_GENERAL_tooltip"                         "If enabled — all players see the same ability pool in the first pick.<br><br>Disabled — every player gets their own random pool.<br>A shared pick makes matches more mirror-like and predictable; a separate one encourages experimentation and build variety."
      "VOTES_LIST_HAS_SKILLS_SELECT_tooltip"                                "Enables the passive hero skill selection stage.<br><br>Skills provide unique effects (passive triggers, ability modifications, etc.) and significantly shape your build. Disabling it speeds up the pre-game flow but removes a layer of customization."
      "VOTES_LIST_ROUND_WHEN_LOSE_AEGIS_tooltip"                            "From which round losing a duel starts draining team aegis charges (lives).<br><br>Before this round, losses do not cost lives — it's the «warm-up phase». The earlier the threshold — the faster the game resolves."
      "VOTES_LIST_ROUND_WHEN_CAN_SUMMON_CREEPS_tooltip"                     "From which round you can start sending creeps to the enemy arena, accelerating their defeat.<br><br>An earlier start empowers aggressive strategies and inter-arena interaction; a later one gives more time for peaceful farming."

