  //=================================================================================================================
    "DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_item_reroll_neutral_book"                                                                             "Neutral Book"
    "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_reroll_neutral_book_Description"                                                                 "<h1>Active: Reroll</h1>You receive another random tier 5 neutral item with charms you can choose yourself.<br><br>Item can be purchased twice, after wave 70 and 80 one charge appears in shop.\n <font color='#f00'>Old item will remain, and all previously obtained neutral items will be available for use. To find them, open shop and click «Neutrals» button in top right corner.</font>"
    "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_revenants_brooch_custom_Description"                                                             "<h1>Active: Phantom Province</h1>Owner's next %number_of_attacks% attacks deal magical damage and cannot miss.<br><br>Allows attacking ethereal units.<br><br><font color='#f00'>Damage calculation considers hero's base damage, bonus damage affects final damage no more than base damage value.</font>"

